ITEM NO.34               COURT NO.11               SECTION III
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
SPECIAL LEAVE PETITION (CIVIL) Diary No(s). 30427/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated  27-06-2024
in R/LPA No. 598/2024 in R/SCA No.4090/2023 passed by the High
Court of Gujarat at Ahmedabad]
CHANDUBHA GAGUBHA JHALA                            Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
STATE OF GUJARAT & ORS.                            Respondent(s)
(IA No. 148914/2025 - CONDONATION OF DELAY IN FILING, IA No.
148915/2025 - EXEMPTION FROM FILING O.T.)
 
Date : 07-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE SUDHANSHU DHULIA
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE JOYMALYA BAGCHI
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s)  Mr. Arpit Gupta, AOR
                   Mr. Divya Pratap Parmar, Adv.
                   
                   
For Respondent(s)  
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
Delay condoned.
We see absolutely no reason to interfere in impugned order
passed by the High Court, in exercise of our jurisdiction under
Article 136 of the Constitution of India.
The present petition is, accordingly, dismissed along with
pending application(s), if any.
(NIRMALA NEGI)                                  (RENU BALA GAMBHIR)
ASTT. REGISTRAR-cum-PS                        ASSISTANT  REGISTRAR
